\"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 597, \"end\": 621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alpensia_Cross-Country_Skiing_Centre_and_Alpensia_Biathlon_Centre\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alpensia Biathlon Centre\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alpensia_Cross-Country_Skiing_Centre_and_Alpensia_Biathlon_Centre\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alpensia_Cross-Country_Skiing_Centre_and_Alpensia_Biathlon_Centre\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The challenges will be expectedly tough, as contenders from frigid countries Norway, Finland, and Sweden lead the 80-strong start list, but Balbanida is ready to soak in lessons from the upcoming experience, win or lose.\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 701, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"score\": 0.9670700358080367, \"rank\": 0.026249294243732887, \"text\": \"Norway\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Norway\"}, {\"begin\": 709, \"end\": 716, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.5701602652959535, \"rank\": 0.7536792587016271, \"text\": \"Finland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Finland_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 728, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9996317868296604, \"rank\": 0.00036647287238584484, \"text\": \"Sweden\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's truly an experience that I want to save here and just like I said before, the chance to ski with the greatest skiers of my age is something of a chance I cannot pass,\\\" said Balbanida, also a taekwondo blackbelter and a roller sports enthusiast.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 1096, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So I am going to take my time and enjoy the moment.\\\"\", \"from\": 1097, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I really want to try my best and I am honored to be here.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pressure?\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It will help me more to be motivated and it gives me more drive.\\\"\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At the bare minimum, Balbanida will try to leave South Korea physically unscathed, as his two compatriots, Fil-Am Peter Groseclose and Fil-Swiss Laetaz Amihan Rabe, both left the country with injuries as souvenirs.\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1337, \"end\": 1348, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999999590243087, \"rank\": 4.0957723716364843e-08, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"score\": 0.9923608910066486, \"rank\": 0.005090782066365987, \"text\": \"Peter\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peter_Griffin\"}, {\"begin\": 1440, \"end\": 1446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Encantadia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.9399449643976866e-13, \"text\": \"Amihan\", \"types\": [\"Q7889\", \"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Encantadia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Encantadia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 16-year-old Groseclose, who competed in the 1500m and 1000m short track speed skating events,crashed and cut his footin his final 500m event, causing him to miss out on a historic medal and finish fifth instead of third.\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1728, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 14-year-old Rabe, meanwhile, only took home to Geneva the positive memory offlag-bearing duties, as she sufferedknee and jaw injuriesbefore she could even compete in the women's free ski slopestyle event.\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1938, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1781, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geneva\", \"score\": 0.9999510803458465, \"rank\": 4.76726944678607e-05, \"text\": \"Geneva\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geneva\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Geneva\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Regardless of the tasks at hand and the perils surrounding Balbanida, his Canada-based Australian coach Allison McArdle just wants her ward to enjoy the entire experience as he gears up for more events in their pipeline.\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 2160, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2027, \"end\": 2037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9603911663360516, \"rank\": 0.04107178886536298, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davey_Allison\", \"score\": 0.9996212495258957, \"rank\": 0.0002746952000248405, \"text\": \"Allison\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davey_Allison\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davey_Allison\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not have a specific\\u00a0goal,\\u00a0we just hope he tries the best he can and enjoy the competition,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am going to continue competing\\u00a0in the World Cups, Junior World Cups and\\u00a0even the world\\u00a0championships,\\\" Balbanida added.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I hope to compete in the 2026 Olympics in Italy.\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2442, \"end\": 2447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8623153669209378, \"rank\": 0.1591661360882777, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got some good racing experience and this competition has really refined my abilities.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2580, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 2582, \"to\": 2591, \"entities\": []}]}"